-- GM Blocks Opel, Peugeot Construction Mid-Class Model: Spiegel
-- B y   J a m e s   K r a u s
-- 2012-09-04T18:06:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-04/gm-blocks-opel-peugeot-construction-mid-class-model-spiegel.html
GM decided not to set up production
platform for next mid-class model with Peugeot,  Spiegel  reports.  The joint project was opposed by management at GM  China  and
Buick over concern French carmaker would compete with their own
models, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
